Pokémon Sword & Shield Type Lookup

This helper is great for Dynamax battles, or quickly seeing which Pokémon will round out your team. All data and images from PokemonDB's Sword & Shield Pokédex. [Toggle instructions]

Click the type tag to select or deselect that type. You can select up to two types. If you select more, the first selection is forgotten.

"Only" is a meta-type which shows Pokémon with only one type. "Clear" resets the selection.

Click a Pokémon's card to see the (calculated) attack and defence values against other types. Click again to close.
